Posts.Content: I have had 3 benign tumors- 2 in one breast and one in the other. I still have a yellow discharge from one and a reddish brown from the other. I starting having the benign tumors in my early twenties and am now 50 and I have had a yearly mammagram since the first tumor was discovered. Have the mammagram to ease your mind.
Posts.Title: Could This be Breast Cancer?
